Introduction

KAACHI was a 3 member British K-pop girl group formed by FrontRow Records. The group consists of Coco, Nicole, and Chunseo. They debuted on April 15th, 2020 with the digital single "Your Turn".

On July 23, 2021, FrontRow Records confirmed that Dani's contract was expired and left the group through a statement.

On March 1, 2023, KAACHI announced their official disbandment.
